quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  7,109,"The nobles/assembly from Pharaoh`s nation said: \"That truly that (is a) knowledgeable magician/sorcerer (E)"
  7,110,"He wants that he brings you out from your land , so what (do) you order/command"
  7,111,"They said: \"Delay/postpone him and his brother and send in the cities/towns gatherers"
  7,112,They come to you with every knowledgeable magician/sorcerer
  7,113,"And the magicians/sorcerers came (to) Pharaoh, and they said: \"That truly for us (is) a reward/fee (E) if we, we were the defeators"
  7,114,"He said: \"Yes, and that you are from (E) the neared/closer"
  7,115,"They said: \"You Moses, either that you throw/throw away, or we, we be the throwing/throwing away"
  7,116,"He said: \"Throw/throw away.\" So when they threw/threw away, they bewitched/enchanted the people`s eyes/sights and they terrorized/terrified them, and they came with great magic/sorcery. (IF GOD REFEREED TO THE MAGIC AS \"GREAT\" THEN IT MUST REALLY HAVE BEEN EXTRAORDINARY BY ANY STANDARD)"
  7,117,"And We inspired/transmitted/signaled to Moses, that throw/throw away your stick/cane, so then it snatches/swallows quickly what they lie/falsify"
  7,118,"So the truth fell/happened , and what they were making/doing (was) wasted/canceled"
  7,119,"So they were defeated/overcome at that place and time, and they turned (became) submissive/subservient"
  7,120,And the magicians/sorcerers were thrown/thrown away prostrating
  7,121,"They said: \"We believed with the creations all together`s/(universes`) Lord"
  7,122,Moses` and Aaron`s Lord
  7,123,"Pharaoh said: \"You believed with Him, before that I permit for you? That, that (is) cheatery/deceit (E) you schemed/cheated/deceived it in the city/town to bring out from it its people , so you will/shall know"
  7,124,"I will cut off/amputate (E) your hands and your feet from opposites , then I will crucify you/place you on crosses all/all together. (\"OPPOSITES\" MEANS A RIGHT HAND AND A LEFT FOOT, OR A LEFT HAND AND A RIGHT FOOT)"
  7,125,"They said: \"We are to our Lord returning"
  7,126,"And you do not revenge/hate/criticize from us except that we believed with our Lord`s evidences/verses/signs, when (it) came to us, our Lord pour on us patience, and make us die (as) Moslems/submitters/surrenderers"